narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned about the research of two other groups. That's it.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: We had 2 very nice talks... except that they were the only two talks for the whole semester (at the beginning and the end of the semester)! I think the faculty can do a better job than that in attracting speakers. Even the student-led seminar series has had more speakers.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: This course is mandatory for all physical chemistry graduate students. There's no choice involved.
